Helpless turtle gets rescued ❤🙌🏼 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @earthfever

Join Brodie Moss and the crew as they explore the remote islands of Australia. This time of year brings in hundreds of mating turtles to the shallows. Right place at the right time allowed the crew to rescue a washed up helpless turtle stuck on her back.

Video by @brodiemoss
🎶 Julius Dreisig & Zeus X Crona - Invisible provided by NoCopyrightSounds
